Package: saAlloc
Type: Package
Title: Optimal Allocation of Sampling Units to Form Strata using Simulated Annealing 
Version: 1.1
Date: 2018-04-23
Author: Jonathan Lisic <jlisic@gmail.com> 
Maintainer: Jonathan Lisic <jlisic@gmail.com> 
Description: A suite of tools to perform joint optimal allocation and stratification
  of sampling units using simulated annealing.  Soft and hard constraints placed on 
  the coefficient of variances (CV) of administrative variables are supported.
  This package was developed with the support of the United States Department of 
  Agriculture National Agricultural Statistics Service. 
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
License: Unlimited 
